sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Caller
    participant A as Algorithms
    participant Q as PriorityQueue
    participant ADJ as Adjacency List

    C->>A: dijkstra(n, edges, src, dst)
    A->>ADJ: Build adjacency list from edges
    A->>Q: add([src, 0])
    loop while !pq.isEmpty()
        A->>Q: poll() → [u, dist]
        alt u == dst
            Q-->>A: found
            A-->>C: dist
        else continue if stale
            A->>A: if dist > best[u] skip
            A->>ADJ: get neighbors
            loop for each neighbor
                A->>A: if dist + w < best[v]
                A->>Q: add([v, newDist])
            end
        end
    end
    A-->>C: -1 (unreachable)

    Note over A,Q: O(E + V log V) with binary heap
